i-11152269%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20busiest%20international%20airport%20in%20Dubai%20was%20hit%20on%20Saturday%20following%20a%20wave%20of%20Iranian%20missile%20attacks%20in%20response%20to%20US-Israel%20strikes%20on%20Tehran%20and%20other%20Iranian%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdubai-international-airport-damaged-in-iranian-strikes-4-injured-video-iran-israel-attack-us-explosions-in-dubai-11152269%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20big%20takeaways%20from%20Sam%20Altman's%20Saturday%20night%20AMA%20on%20OpenAI's%20Pentagon%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223695%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sam%20altman%20staring%20at%20camera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a393801fb3fcb42648af30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Atlman%20caught%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20deep%20reflection.%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESam%20Altman%20went%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday%20night%20and%20told%20users%20to%20ask%20him%20anything%20about%20OpenAI's%20Pentagon%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAltman%20on%20Friday%20night%20announced%20that%20OpenAI%20will%20work%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20let%20it%20use%20its%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%20five%20big%20takeaways%20from%20Altman's%20AMA%20session.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Altman%20hopped%20onto%20X%20on%20Saturday%20night%20and%20told%20users%20to%20ask%20him%20anything%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-shares-contract-language-department-of-war-mass-surveillance-weapons-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%2C%20late%20on%20Friday%2C%20announced%20that%20his%20company%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ai-deal-sam-altman-pentagon-defense-department-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efinalized%20a%20deal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20to%20use%20its%20AI%20models.%20OpenAI's%20deal%20came%20after%20Anthropic%20refused%20an%20ultimatum%20regarding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei-pentagon-free-speech-patriots-american-values-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eterms%20of%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20frontier%20model%2C%20Claude%2C%20for%20deployment%20in%20mass%20domestic%20surveillance%20and%20fully%20autonomous%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%205%20big%20takeaways%20from%20Altman's%20AMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20OpenAI-Pentagon%20deal%20was%20'rushed%2C'%20and%20Altman%20knows%20the%20'optics'%20don't%20look%20good%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20deal%20was%20done%20quickly%20in%20%26quot%3Ban%20attempt%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20in%20a%20separate%20post%20that%20the%20deal%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Brushed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Boptics%20don't%20look%20good%26quot%3B%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20are%20right%20and%20this%20does%20lead%20to%20a%20de-escalation%20between%20the%20DoW%20and%20the%20industry%2C%20we%20will%20look%20like%20geniuses%2C%20and%20a%20company%20that%20took%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%20to%20do%20things%20to%20help%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20not%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20characterized%20as%20rushed%20and%20uncareful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20added%20that%20he%20sees%20%26quot%3Bpromising%20signs%26quot%3B%20for%20where%20this%20will%20all%20land%20for%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOpenAI%20took%20the%20Pentagon%20deal%20because%20it%20'got%20comfortable'%20with%20the%20'contract%20language'%3Cp%3EAltman%20was%20asked%20why%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20went%20with%20OpenAI%20over%20Anthropic.%20He%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20speak%20for%20his%20competitor%2C%20but%20did%20speculate%20on%20why%20OpenAI%20got%20the%20contract%20inked%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20I%20saw%20reporting%20that%20they%20were%20extremely%20close%20on%20a%20deal%2C%20and%20for%20much%20of%20the%20time%20both%20sides%20really%20wanted%20to%20reach%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20what%20happens%20in%20tense%20negotiations%20when%20things%20get%20stressed%20and%20deteriorate%20super%20fast%2C%20and%20I%20could%20believe%20that%20was%20a%20large%20part%20of%20what%20happened%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20OpenAI%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20%26quot%3Bgot%20comfortable%20with%20the%20contractual%20language%26quot%3B%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Anthropic%20may%20have%20wanted%20more%20operational%20control%20than%20we%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOpenAI%20has%203%20redlines%2C%20but%20it's%20open%20to%20changing%20them%20as%20tech%20evolves%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-shares-contract-language-department-of-war-mass-surveillance-weapons-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20has%20%26quot%3Bthree%20redlines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20those%20redlines%20could%20change%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20could%20be%20more%20of%20them%20put%20in%20place%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20technology%20evolves%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bnew%20risks%26quot%3B%20come%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20a%20really%20important%20point%3A%20we%20are%20not%20elected.%20We%20have%20a%20democratic%20process%20where%20we%20do%20elect%20our%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20expertise%20with%20the%20technology%20and%20understand%20its%20limitations%2C%20but%20I%20think%20you%20should%20be%20terrified%20of%20a%20private%20company%20deciding%20on%20what%20is%20and%20isn't%20ethical%20in%20the%20most%20important%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeems%20fine%20for%20us%20to%20decide%20how%20ChatGPT%20should%20respond%20to%20a%20controversial%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20really%20don't%20want%20us%20to%20decide%20what%20to%20do%20if%20a%20nuke%20is%20coming%20towards%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAltman%20says%20Anthropic%20is%20on%20a%20'dangerous'%20path%3Cp%3EAltman%20said%20OpenAI%20had%20been%20talking%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20for%20%26quot%3Bmany%20months%26quot%3B%20about%20non-classified%20work%2C%20before%20%26quot%3Bthings%20shifted%20into%20high%20gear%20on%20the%20classified%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20DoW%20to%20be%20flexible%20on%20what%20we%20needed%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20support%20them%20in%20their%20very%20important%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20current%20path%20things%20are%20on%20is%20dangerous%20for%20Anthropic%2C%20healthy%20competition%2C%20and%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20X%20as%20well.%20%26quot%3BWe%20negotiated%20to%20make%20sure%20similar%20terms%20would%20be%20offered%20to%20all%20other%20AI%20labs.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20also%20asked%20for%20%26quot%3Bsome%20empathy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20given%20its%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20important%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20Altman's%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EOur%20industry%20tells%20them%20%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20we%20are%20building%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20high%20order%20bit%20in%20geopolitical%20conflict.%20China%20is%20rushing%20ahead.%20You%20are%20very%20behind.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAnd%20then%20we%20say%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20won't%20help%20you%2C%20and%20we%20think%20you%20are%20kind%20of%20evil.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20don't%20think%20I'd%20react%20great%20in%20that%20situation.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20do%20not%20believe%20unelected%20leaders%20of%20private%20companies%20should%20have%20as%20much%20power%20as%20our%20democratically%20elected%20government.%20But%20I%20do%20think%20we%20need%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAltman%20says%20AI%20can%20help%20counter%20big%20security%20threats%20on%20two%20fronts%3Cp%3EAltman%20says%20AI%20could%20come%20in%20useful%20on%20two%20fronts.%20Firstly%2C%20the%20US's%20%26quot%3Bability%20to%20defend%20against%20major%20cyber%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20particularly%2C%20an%20attack%20that%20might%20take%20down%20the%20country's%20electrical%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20biosecurity%20is%20an%20area%20where%20AI%20could%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20think%20we%20are%20currently%20set%20up%20well%20enough%20to%20detect%20and%20respond%20to%20a%20novel%20pandemic%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftakeaways-sam-altman-openai-pentagon-deal-ask-me-anything-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772329009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a39393fd4fbd083f2949bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftakeaways-sam-altman-openai-pentagon-deal-ask-me-anything-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman%20answered%20questions%20from%20users%20on%20X%20on%20OpenAI's%20red%20lines%20and%20talked%20about%20why%20the%20company's%20deal%20with%20the%20Pentagon%20happened%20so%20fast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cteh%40businessinsider.com%20(Cheryl