quot%3B%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20our%20agreement%20has%20more%20guardrails%20than%20any%20previous%20agreement%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-ai-military-use-dario-amodei-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclassified%20AI%20deployments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Anthropic's%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI's%20post%20read.%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20agreement%2C%20we%20protect%20our%20red%20lines%20through%20a%20more%20expansive%2C%20multi-layered%20approach.%20We%20retain%20full%20discretion%20over%20our%20safety%20stack%2C%20we%20deploy%20via%20cloud%2C%20cleared%20OpenAI%20personnel%20are%20in%20the%20loop%2C%20and%20we%20have%20strong%20contractual%20protections.%20This%20is%20all%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20strong%20existing%20protections%20in%20U.S.%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20took%20to%20social%20media%20shortly%20after%20the%20company's%20blog%20post%20was%20published%2C%20answering%20questions%20from%20users%20concerned%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20OpenAI's%20agreement%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Ask-Me-Anything-style%20responses%2C%20he%20doubled%20down%20on%20OpenAI's%20agreement%20being%20better%20than%20Anthropic's%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20broader%20AI%20landscape%20but%20also%20for%20the%20American%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnthropic%20seemed%20more%20focused%20on%20specific%20prohibitions%20in%20the%20contract%2C%20rather%20than%20citing%20applicable%20laws%2C%20which%20we%20felt%20comfortable%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20about%20why%20OpenAI%20agreed%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20government%20when%20its%20rival%20would%20not.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Anthropic%20may%20have%20wanted%20more%20operational%20control%20than%20we%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20agreement%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Anthropic%20being%20blacklisted%20and%20declared%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-department-of-war-pete-hegseth-military-contract-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20refusing%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20military's%20terms%20of%20use%20for%20the%20company's%20frontier%20model%2C%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%2C%20in%20a%20Friday%20statement%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20amount%20of%20intimidation%20or%20punishment%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20War%20will%20change%20our%20position%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-federal-agencies-stop-using-anthropic-technology-department-defense-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emass%20domestic%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20fully%20autonomous%20weapons%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bchallenge%20any%20supply%20chain%20risk%20designation%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20in%20its%20Saturday%20post%2C%20argued%20that%20Anthropic%20should%20not%20be%20designated%20as%20a%20supply%20chain%20risk%20and%20said%20it%20had%20made%20its%20position%20%26quot%3Bclear%20to%20the%20government.%26quot%3B%20Its%20agreement%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20War%20stemmed%2C%20in%20part%2C%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20%26quot%3Bde-escalate%20things%20between%20DoW%20and%20the%20US%20AI%20labs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20future%20is%20going%20to%20require%20real%20and%20deep%20collaboration%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20AI%20labs%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI's%20post%20reads.%20%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20our%20deal%20here%2C%20we%20asked%20that%20the%20same%20terms%20be%20made%20available%20to%20all%20AI%20labs%2C%20and%20specifically%20that%20the%20government%20would%20try%20to%20resolve%20things%20with%20Anthropic%3B%20the%20current%20state%20is%20a%20very%20bad%20way%20to%20kick%20off%20this%20next%20phase%20of%20collaboration%20between%20the%20government%20and%20AI%20labs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20Anthropic%2C%20or%20any%20other%20leading%20AI%20company%2C%20had%20been%20offered%20similar%20contractual%20terms%20to%20those%20that%20OpenAI%20said%20it%20had%20agreed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20said%20that%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20deal%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20War%2C%20it%20will%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bfull%20control%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20safety%20stack%20it%20deploys%2C%20and%20robust%20%26quot%3Bsafety%20guardrails%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20misuse.%20Should%20the%20government%20violate%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bcould%26quot%3B%20terminate%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20expect%20that%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20said%20in%20its%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%2C%20in%20his%20Ask%20Me%20Anything%20posts%2C%20wrote%20that%20OpenAI%20would%20not%20agree%20to%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20use%20its%20technology%20for%20mass%20domestic%20surveillance%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20it%20violates%20the%20constitution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20is%20prepared%20for%20a%20potential%20dispute%20over%20the%20legality%20of%20specific%20governmental%20requests%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20added%20that%20if%20the%20Constitution%20were%20amended%20to%20make%20such%20surveillance%20legal%2C%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20I%20would%20quit%20my%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20very%20deeply%20believe%20in%20the%20democratic%20process%2C%20and%20that%20our%20elected%20leaders%20have%20the%20power%2C%20and%20that%20we%20all%20have%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20terrified%20of%20a%20world%20where%20AI%20companies%20act%20like%20they%20have%20more%20power%20than%20the%20government.%20I%20would%20also%20be%20terrified%20of%20a%20world%20where%20our%20government%20decided%20mass%20domestic%20surveillance%20was%20ok.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20I'd%20come%20to%20work%20every%20day%20if%20that%20were%20the%20state%20of%20the%20country%2FConstitution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20AI%20giants%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20criticism%2C%20with%20critics%20concerned%20about%20the%20ethical%20implications%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20War's%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20OpenAI's%20agreement%20to%20provide%20the%20government%20access%20to%20its%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20on%20Saturday%20said%20it%20believes%20AI%20will%20%26quot%3Bintroduce%20new%20risks%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20by%20allowing%20the%20government%20use%20of%20its%20models%2C%20will%20give%20people%20defending%20national%20security%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20tools%26quot%3B%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-number-one-app-store-openai-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20model%2C%20Claude%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shot%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20app%20store%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20many%20people%20on%20social%20media%2C%20including%20celebrities%20like%20Katy%20Perry%2C%20have%20publicly%20posted%20about%20canceling%20their%20ChatGPT%20subscriptions%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20OpenAI's%20agreement%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-shares-contract-language-department-of-war-mass-surveillance-weapons-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772327786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a373821fb3fcb42648ae55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-shares-contract-