20the%20%2420-per-month%20%26quot%3BPro%26quot%3B%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Edone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FDkS9DmlUAR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FDkS9DmlUAR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20KATY%20PERRY%20(%40katyperry)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkatyperry%2Fstatus%2F2027619173325553765%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20X%20user%2C%20Adam%20Lyttle%2C%20wrote%20%26quot%3BMade%20the%20switch%2C%26quot%3B%20alongside%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20email%20inbox%20with%20a%20receipt%20from%20Anthropic%20and%20cancellation%20confirmation%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMade%20the%20switch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Flm8xh48xDj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Flm8xh48xDj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Adam%20Lyttle%20(%40adamlyttleapps)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadamlyttleapps%2Fstatus%2F2027648432870150578%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit's%20ChatGPT%20subreddit%2C%20dozens%20of%20users%20say%20they've%20deleted%20their%20accounts%20and%20are%20urging%20others%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCancel%20ChatGPT%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20a%20common%20refrain%20online%2C%20while%20some%20users%20have%20taken%20a%20more%20personal%20tone%2C%20saying%20Altman's%20move%20%26quot%3Bcrossed%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20hasn't%20polarized%20all%20AI%20users%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20Reddit%20thread%2C%20several%20commenters%20said%20the%20news%20does%20not%20affect%20their%20choice%20of%20AI%20model%2C%20arguing%20that%20Anthropic's%20work%20with%20Palantir%20raises%20similar%20concerns.%20In%20November%202024%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20Palantir%2C%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20struck%20an%20agreement%20to%20provide%20US%20intelligence%20and%20defense%20agencies%20access%20to%20Claude%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20said%20he%20would%20designate%20Anthropic%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsupply%20chain%20risk%20to%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bchallenge%20any%20supply%20chain%20risk%20designation%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Friday%20post%2C%20Altman%20said%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20had%20agreed%20with%20two%20of%20OpenAI's%20safety%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20of%20our%20most%20important%20safety%20principles%20are%20prohibitions%20on%20domestic%20mass%20surveillance%20and%20human%20responsibility%20for%20the%20use%20of%20force%2C%20including%20for%20autonomous%20weapon%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThe%20DoW%20agrees%20with%20these%20principles%2C%20reflects%20them%20in%20law%20and%20policy%2C%20and%20we%20put%20them%20into%20our%20agreement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20OpenAI%20published%20a%20more%20detailed%20description%20of%20its%20contract%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20including%20the%20specific%20language%20it%20used%20surrounding%20the%20use%20of%20its%20models%20for%20surveillance%20and%20autonomous%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20topic%20of%20autonomous%20weapons%2C%20OpenAI%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20AI%20System%20will%20not%20be%20used%20to%20independently%20direct%20autonomous%20weapons%20in%20any%20case%20where%20law%2C%20regulation%2C%20or%20Department%20policy%20requires%20human%20control%2C%20nor%20will%20it%20be%20used%20to%20assume%20other%20high-stakes%20decisions%20that%20require%20approval%20by%20a%20human%20decisionmaker%20under%20the%20same%20authorities.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20topic%20of%20mass%20surveillance%2C%20OpenAI%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20AI%20System%20shall%20not%20be%20used%20for%20unconstrained%20monitoring%20of%20U.S.%20persons'%20private%20information%20as%20consistent%20with%20these%20authorities.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20chatbot%20users%20suggested%20it's%20all%20fair%20in%20business%2C%20war%2C%20and%20federal%20procurement%2C%20others%20suggested%20the%20Pentagon's%20stance%20may%20have%20handed%20Anthropic%20a%20public%20relations%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20user%20Tae%20Kim%20joked%20that%20Hegseth%20might%20need%20a%20new%20title%3A%20%26quot%3BSecretary%20Hegseth%20Chief%20of%20Claude%20Marketing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-number-one-app-store-openai-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772322862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a36d7ad3e2f1aef369c086%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-number-one-app-store-openai-chatgpt-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20secured%20a%20Pentagon%20deal%2C%20sparking%20backlash%20and%20shifting%20some%20users'%20loyalties%20to%20Anthropic's%20rival%20Claude%20chatbot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-hits-