on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20and%20Israel%20pushed%20for%20Iranian%20regime%20change%20ahead%20of%20the%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20was%20killed%20during%20the%20massive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-us-strike-iran-preemptive-defense-chief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20US-Israeli%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKhamenei%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20evil%20people%20in%20History%2C%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20unable%20to%20avoid%20our%20Intelligence%20and%20Highly%20Sophisticated%20Tracking%20Systems%20and%2C%20working%20closely%20with%20Israel%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20thing%20he%2C%20or%20the%20other%20leaders%20that%20have%20been%20killed%20along%20with%20him%2C%20could%20do.%20This%20is%20the%20single%20greatest%20chance%20for%20the%20Iranian%20people%20to%20take%20back%20their%20Country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20X%20account%20for%20Khamenei%20confirmed%20his%20death%20shortly%20thereafter%2C%20with%20a%20post%20in%20Persian%20which%2C%20when%20translated%2C%20read%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20name%20of%20Nami%20Haider%20(peace%20be%20upon%20him).%26quot%3B%20Iranian%20state%20media%20reported%20on%20his%20death%20early%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22fa%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22rtl%5C%22%3E%D8%A8%D9%87%20%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%20%D9%86%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%20%D8%AD%DB%8C%D8%AF%D8%B1%20%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%87%E2%80%8C%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%85%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn848j6KASq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fn848j6KASq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20KHAMENEI.IR%20%7C%20%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B3%DB%8C%20(%40Khamenei_fa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKhamenei_fa%2Fstatus%2F2027858979250946330%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKhamenei%2C%2086%2C%20was%20in%20power%20for%20almost%2040%20years%2C%20and%20his%20reign%20was%20marked%20by%20high%20tensions%20with%20the%20US%20and%20the%20West%20more%20broadly%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20recent%20brutal%20crackdown%20on%20Iranians%20protesting%20high%20inflation.%20Tensions%20with%20the%20US%20have%20centered%20on%20Iran's%20longstanding%20support%20for%20terrorism%20and%20its%20pursuit%20of%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20as%20the%20US%20urged%20Iran%20to%20make%20a%20new%20nuclear%20deal%2C%20the%20American%20military%20has%20been%20building%20up%20its%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20buildup%20has%20been%20accompanied%20by%20heated%20rhetoric%20and%20warnings%20from%20both%20Washington%20and%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMissiles%20struck%20several%20high-value%20targets%20in%20and%20around%20Tehran%2C%20including%20Khamenei's%20compound%20near%20Tehran%20and%20his%20offices%20in%20the%20capital.%20Khamenei's%20location%20during%20the%20strikes%20was%20previously%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-trump-full-speech-announcing-strikes-on-iran-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20video%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20the%20start%20of%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20combat%20operations%26quot%3B%20against%20Iran%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20the%20president%20called%20for%20Iranian%20citizens%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20over%20your%20government.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20probably%20your%20only%20chance%20for%20generations.%26quot%3B%20Trump%20has%20recently%20made%20similar%20comments%20in%20favor%20of%20regime%20change%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20issued%20threats%20against%20Khamenei.%20In%20June%202025%2C%20after%20joint%20US-Israeli%20strikes%20on%20Iran%2C%20Israel's%20Defense%20Minister%20Israel%20Katz%20said%20Khamenei%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20continue%20to%20exist%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20him%20a%20dictator.%20Other%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20like%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20have%20made%20similar%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhamenei%20became%20Supreme%20Leader%20in%201989%2C%20acting%20as%20the%20ultimate%20authority%20across%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20Iranian%20government%20and%20the%20military.%20Khamenei%20was%20also%20the%20country's%20religious%20leader%20and%20was%20granted%20the%20title%20of%20ayatollah%2C%20a%20title%20for%20high-ranking%20clerics%20in%20Shia%20Islam%2C%20Iran's%20official%20state%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20death%20marks%20a%20major%20upheaval%20amid%20US%20combat%20operations%20against%20Iran%2C%20which%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20said%20was%20aimed%20at%20eliminating%20imminent%20threats%20to%20Americans%20and%20Israelis.%20The%20American%20operation%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BEpic%20Fury%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20involved%20a%20mixture%20of%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20assets%2C%20including%20Tomahawk%20missiles%2C%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20Systems%2C%20and%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20Khamenei's%20death%20will%20affect%20the%20fate%20of%20Iran's%20regime%2C%20which%20is%20bolstered%20by%20the%20hardline%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20and%20a%20vast%20internal%20security%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-missiles-multiple-countries-what-happened-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIran's%20retaliatory%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20targeted%20US%20bases%20across%20the%20region%2C%20with%20US%20assets%20and%20partner%20force