3D%5C%222826%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20and%20white%20aerial%20footage%20shows%20a%20large%20aircraft%20on%20tarmac%20with%20the%20word%20'Unclassified'%20written%20on%20the%20top%20in%20large%2C%20neon-green%20letters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a34a57d3e2f1aef369bfa3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20shared%20footage%20of%20strikes%20on%20Iranian%20targets.%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%2FX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20shared%20new%20video%20footage%20from%20its%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20and%20Israel%20launched%20strikes%20with%20hundreds%20of%20aircraft%20and%20numerous%20munitions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20footage%20includes%20missiles%20launched%20at%20sea%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20Iranian%20targets%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20US%20video%20footage%20shows%20elements%20of%20its%20strikes%20on%20Iran%2C%20including%20the%20launching%20of%20missiles%20and%20fighters%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20multiple%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20footage%20shared%20by%20US%20Central%20Command%20on%20Saturday%20shows%20destroyers%20firing%20missiles%20at%20sea%20and%20carriers%20launching%20combat%20aircraft.%20It%20also%20shows%20repeated%20strikes%20on%20Iranian%20military%20targets.%20It%20said%20its%20forces%20are%20%26quot%3Bdelivering%20an%20overwhelming%20and%20unrelenting%20blow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20President%20stated%2C%20our%20objective%20is%20to%20defend%20the%20American%20people%20by%20eliminating%20imminent%20threats%20from%20the%20Iranian%20regime.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20President%20ordered%20bold%20action.%20CENTCOM%20forces%20are%20delivering%20an%20overwhelming%20and%20unrelenting%20blow.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FB0k5gV4YnU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FB0k5gV4YnU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20U.S.%20Central%20Command%20(%40CENTCOM)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCENTCOM%2Fstatus%2F2027814907119321481%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20did%20not%20specify%20exactly%20what%20was%20hit%2C%20or%20attribute%20each%20attack%20to%20the%20US%20or%20Israel%2C%20which%20jointly%20took%20part%20in%20the%20operation%2C%20dubbed%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20on%20the%20American%20side%20and%20Roaring%20Lion%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20operation%2C%20which%20started%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20involved%20precision%20munitions%20launched%20from%20the%20air%2C%20land%2C%20and%20sea%2C%20and%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Binvolves%20the%20largest%20regional%20concentration%20of%20American%20military%20firepower%20in%20a%20generation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20official%20also%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20US%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-tomahawk-cruise-missiles-trump-may-send-ukraine-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETomahawk%20cruise%20missiles%20from%20warships%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20ground%20forces%20used%20the%20High%20Mobility%20Artillery%20Rocket%20System%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-member-estonia-doubling-down-us-made-himars-ukraine-success-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHIMARS%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Other%20weapons%20were%20also%20employed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20said%20that%20it%20used%20around%20200%20fighters%20in%20what%20it%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20largest%20military%20flyover%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20jets%20dropped%20hundreds%20of%20munitions%20%26quot%3Btargeting%20approximately%20500%20objectives%2C%20including%20aerial%20defense%20systems%20and%20missile%20launchers%2C%20in%20a%20number%20of%20locations%20in%20Iran%2C%20simultaneously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-video-strikes-iran-missile-launcher-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20released%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20an%20attack%20on%20missile%20launchers%20at%20a%20remote%20site%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20said%20attacks%20were%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bdismantle%20the%20Iranian%20regime's%20security%20apparatus%2C%20prioritizing%20locations%20that%20posed%20an%20imminent%20threat.%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Iran's%20missile%20program%20and%20other%20military%20capabilities%20and%20said%20that%20the%20aim%20was%20for%20Iran%20to%20%26quot%3Bnever%26quot%3B%20have%20a%20nuclear%20weapon.%20He%20called%20on%20Iranian%20forces%20to%20surrender%20or%20face%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grey%20smoke%20plume%20in%20a%20blue%20sky%20over%20buildings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a340b1fd4fbd083f2947a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3A%20Smoke%20rises%20after%20Iran%20launched%20a%20missile%20attack%20in%20Bahrain.%3Cp%3EStringer%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECENTCOM%20said%20targets%20included%20%26quot%3BIslamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%20command%20and%20control%20facilities%2C%20Iranian%20air%20defense%20capabilities%2C%20missile%20and%20drone%20launch%20sites%2C%20and%20military%20airfields.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrikes%20have%20been%20reported%20across%20Iran%2C%20including%20at%20military%20sites%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-images-show-damage-iranian-supreme-leader-residence-tehran-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresidence%20of%20Iran's%20supreme%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Satellite%20imagery%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatellite-images-show-iranian-warship-burning-after-us-israel-strikes-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshowed%20a%20burning%20Iranian%20warship%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20initial%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIranian%20officials%20said%20that%20at%20least%2085%20people%20were%20killed%20at%20a%20girls'%20elementary%20school%2C%20and%20the%20Iranian%20Red%20Crescent%20humanitarian%20group%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20201%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20start%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Israeli%20strikes%2C%20Iran%20launched%20counterattacks%20against%20Israel%20and%20against%20multiple%20nearby%20nations%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20bases%20that%20host%20US%20forces%20and%20are%20US%20allies.%20Those%20nations%20reported%20many%20successful%20interceptions%2C%20but%20also%20some%20damage.%20Details%20about%20Iran's%20attacks%20are%20still%20emerging%2C%20and%20attacks%20may%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECENTCOM%20said%20that%20its%20forces%20had%20successfully%20defended%20against%20hundreds%20of%20Iranian%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks.%20It%20said%20there%20was%20damage%20to%20US%20military%20facilities%2C%20but%20that%20it%20was%20minimal%20and%20did%20not%20impact%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBahrain%20said%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20US%20Navy's%205th%20Fleet%2C%20located%20in%20the%20country%2C%20was%20hit%20by%20an%20Iranian%20missile%20attack%2C%20without%20giving%20details%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20any%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20strikes%20also%20targeted%20Kuwait%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Qatar%2C%20and%20Jordan.%20Some%20countries%20reported%20injuries%20from%20falling%20debris%2C%20including%20Kuwait%2C%20which%20said%20that%20three%20armed%20forces%20members%20had%20minor%20injuries%20from%20shrapnel%20from%20the%20interception%20of%20drones%20and%20ballistic%20missiles.%20The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20said%20one%20person%20was%20killed%20by%20falling%20debris%20in%20its%20capital%2C%20and%20four%20people%20were%20injured%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20an%20incident%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Dubai%20that%20is%20known%20for%20luxury%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Abbas%20Araghchi%20called%20the%20US%20and%20Israeli%20strikes%20%26quot%3Bwholly%20unprovoked%2C%20illegal%2C%20and%20illegitimate.%26quot%3B%20Iran%20has%20vowed%20further%20action%2C%20and%20Israel%20has%20hinted%20that%20its%20actions%20so%20far%20only%20represent%20the%20beginning%20of%20its%20operation.%20The%20US%20has%20indicated%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-on-iran-flights-canceled-diverted-busiest-airspace-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFlights%20have%20been%20cancelled%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20region%2C%20and%20multiple%20countries%20have%20closed%20their%20airspaces%2C%20resulting%20in%20major%20disruption%20for%20what%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20busiest%20flight%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-shares-video-of-its-iran-strikes-including-destroying-targets-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772309290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a34ac7d3e2f1aef369bfa5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-shares-video-of-its-iran-strikes-including-destroying-targets-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US