D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fground-stop-issued-newark-airport-over-staffing-issues-faa-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENewark%20Airport%20in%20Jersey%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20San%20Francisco.%20My%20business-class%20seat%20had%20been%20booked%20by%20a%20clothing%20brand%20I%20had%20been%20working%20for%20at%20the%20time.%20My%20seat%20on%20row%2011%20was%20a%20window%20seat%20with%20my%20own%20little%20nook%2C%20a%20treat%20for%20me%2C%20who%20usually%20flies%20in%20the%20economy%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20settled%20in%2C%20neatly%20arranging%20my%20things%20in%20the%20compartment%20above%20my%20head%20and%20around%20my%20seat%2C%20a%20woman%20I%20didn't%20recognize%20kindly%20asked%20if%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-you-switch-seats-on-plane-flight-attendant-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewould%20mind%20switching%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20her%20so%20she%20could%20sit%20next%20to%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quickly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSure.%26quot%3B%20I%20know%20that%20in%20economy%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20question%20can%20produce%20mixed%20feelings%2C%20because%20if%20you've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwindow-seat-best-place-to-sit-plane-health-experts-say-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebooked%20a%20window%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20want%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20middle%20seat.%20But%20in%20business%20class%2C%20all%20the%20seats%20are%20good%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e97928e5-4285-4233-8fff-643f19e1ba2a%5C%22%3EI%20hadn't%20realized%20who%20her%20husband%20was%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20I%20responded%20to%20her%20request%2C%20I%20looked%20up%20and%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-lasting-male-celebrity-friendships-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKeegan-Michael%20Key%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20switching%20seats%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20so%20she%20could%20sit%20next%20to%20him.%20She%20continued%2C%20explaining%20she%20thought%20she%20had%20booked%20them%20to%20sit%20next%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20her%20seat%20in%20row%2010%2C%20and%20she%20took%20mine%20in%20row%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20not%20only%20did%20I%20get%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-airlines-flying-business-class-delta-one-fiji-airways-traveler-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20in%20business%20class%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20already%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20also%20got%20to%20travel%20in%20front%20of%20a%20celebrity%20that%20I%20absolutely%20love.%20He's%20literally%20one%20of%20my%20favourite%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Keegan-Michael%20Key%20on%20a%20plane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699c9c0c2237a6a8f0cdaa86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDenny%20Balmaceda%20sat%20right%20in%20front%20of%20Keegan-Michael%20Key%20on%20a%20plane.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Denny%20Balmaceda%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20leaned%20over%20and%20said%20Key%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20take%20a%20photo%20with%20me.%20He%20did%2C%20and%20he%20was%20so%20nice.%20Throughout%20the%20flight%2C%20he%20was%20the%20same%20with%20everyone%20who%20came%20up%20to%20him%20%E2%80%94%20a%20real%20gentleman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f351f3d2-f83f-44c6-80de-22bbac29c125%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20so%20nice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20single%20person%20who%20came%20up%20to%20him%20got%20his%20time%20and%20never%20once%20seemed%20annoyed.%20He%20talked%20to%20everyone%20and%20let%20people%20take%20photos%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20wife%20needed%20help%20with%20anything%2C%20he%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20the%20flight%20came%20to%20an%20end%2C%20I%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20grab%20my%20bag%2C%20and%20he%20didn't%20flinch%20%E2%80%94%20he%20was%20fine%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20sense%20that%20he%20thought%20he%20was%20above%20anyone%20on%20that%20plane.%20He%20was%20just%20a%20real%20person%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20a%20celebrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%20I%20know%20there%20are%20both%20celebrities%20who%20are%20rude%20and%20those%20who%20just%20have%20bad%20days.%20I%20know%20that%20sometimes%2C%20people%20just%20want%20to%20be%20themselves%20without%20the%20fame.%20They%20just%20want%20to%20travel%20on%20planes%20and%20not%20be%20recognized.%20But%20he%20didn't%20fit%20into%20any%20of%20these%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20flight%20landed%20and%20before%20we%20went%20our%20separate%20ways%2C%20I%20took%20a%20couple%20of%20photos%20of%20us%20together%20to%20show%20my%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20one-in-a-million%20chance%20that%20I'd%20switch%20seats%20with%20someone%20famous%2C%20and%20I%20was%20very%20happy%20and%20surprised%20to%20get%20to%20experience%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-met-keegan-michael-key-on-a-plane-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772307481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699c89352237a6a8f0cda77e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-met-keegan-michael-key-on-a-plane-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20traveler%20shares%20what%20happened%20after%20switching%20seats%20with%20Keegan-Michael%20Key's%20wife%20on%20a%20business-class%20flight%20from%20Newark%20to%20San%20Francisco.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Crosby%20Medlicott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-met-keegan-michael-key-on-a-plane-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%2