p%3EHere's%20what%20to%20watch%20as%20investors%20react%20to%20the%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274b2657b-4d42-4158-80ab-2f2838c35d96%5C%22%3E'Worst%20fears'%20for%20oil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOil%20markets%20might%20have%20to%20face%20their%20worst%20fears%20on%20Monday.%20As%20things%20stand%20right%20now%2C%20we%20think%20Brent%20could%20hit%20%24100%2Fb%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclays%20analysts%20wrote%20on%20Saturday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20potential%20effect%20on%20oil%20markets%20is%20hard%20to%20overstate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20said%20investors%20should%20expect%20oil%20prices%20to%20test%20the%20%24100%20per%20barrel%20level%20on%20Monday%2C%20which%20would%20represent%20a%2037%25%20spike%20from%20Friday's%20close%20of%20%2467.02.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20were%20already%20on%20edge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-supply-shock-brent-crude-iran-venezuela-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eover%20a%20potential%20%26quot%3Boil%20shock%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20after%20the%20attack%20on%20Venezuela%20and%20amid%20simmering%20tensions%20with%20Iran.%20Crude%20prices%20have%20crept%20up%20steadily%20in%202026%20after%20tumbling%20last%20year.%20Brent%2C%20the%20international%20benchmark%2C%20is%20up%2020%25%20year-to-date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rapid%20rise%20in%20energy%20prices%20would%20also%20ratchet%20up%20inflation%20expectations%2C%20potentially%20weighing%20on%20business%20activity%20and%20consumer%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20positive%20supply%20shock%20to%20oil%20prices%20would%20materially%20impact%20inflation%20expectations%20and%20inflation%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20Deutsche%20Bank%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20before%20this%20weekend's%20attack%2C%20adding%20that%20an%20oil%20shock%20is%20a%20key%20risk%20to%20their%20economic%20outlook%20for%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20predicted%20last%20year%20that%20a%20serious%20conflic