ard.%20Rocket%20alert.%20A%20wailing%20tone%20settles%20over%20the%20city.%20Within%20seconds%2C%20the%20movement%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20this%20early%20Sabbath%20morning%20changes.%20Cars%20stop%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20intersections.%20Doors%20slam%20shut.%20Those%20who%20cannot%20reach%20a%20public%20shelter%20disappear%20into%20stairwells%20or%20underground%20parking%20garages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20still%20hold%20their%20phones%20in%20their%20hands%2C%20others%20carry%20shopping%20bags%2C%20or%20have%20come%20out%20of%20their%20apartments%20barefoot.%20Some%20have%20panic%20written%20across%20their%20faces%20%E2%80%94%20because%20normally%20the%20Home%20Command%20app%20warns%20ten%20to%2015%20minutes%20before%20a%20missile%20from%20Iran%20could%20reach%20Tel%20Aviv.%20But%20this%20morning%2C%20that%20advance%20warning%20did%20not%20come.%20From%20the%20moment%20the%20sirens%20sound%2C%20only%2060%20to%20at%20most%2090%20seconds%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20that%20morning%2C%20Israel%20had%20carried%20out%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-us-strike-iran-preemptive-defense-chief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge-scale%20military%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20targets%20in%20Iran.%20According%20to%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20it%20was%20a%20preemptive%20attack%20intended%20to%20weaken%20Iran's%20military%20and%20nuclear%20capabilities.%20Explosions%20were%20reported%20from%20Tehran%20as%20well%20as%20several%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israeli%20security%20sources%2C%20the%20targets%20included%20facilities%20belonging%20to%20the%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20as%20well%20as%20sites%20in%20the%20immediate%20vicinity%20of%20political%20power%20centers.%20As%20recently%20as%20Friday%20evening%2C%20Israeli%20security%20expert%20Sima%20Shine%20had%20told%20WELT%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20close%20to%20a%20war.%20But%20Israel%20is%20prepared.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20declared%20that%20the%20goal%20of%20the%20operation%20had%20been%20to%20eliminate%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20threat.%26quot%3B%20Israel%20had%20acted%20to%20prevent%20Iran%20from%20further%20expanding%20its%20military%20capabilities.%20Furthermore%2C%20military%20pressure%20could%20enable%20Iranians%20to%20%26quot%3Btopple%20the%20regime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EU.S.%20authorities%20subsequently%20confirmed%20that%20American%20forces%20had%20participated%20%E2%80%94%20both%20from%20the%20air%20and%20from%20the%20sea.%20The%20Iranian%20leadership%20responded%20immediately.%20State%20media%20announced%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrushing%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20stating%20that%20Israeli%20and%20American%20military%20bases%20would%20now%20be%20considered%20legitimate%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterward%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-missiles-multiple-countries-what-happened-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecounterattack%20began%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20rockets%20and%20drones%20were%20fired%20toward%20Israel.%20Sirens%20wailed%20across%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20millions%20of%20people%20were%20instructed%20to%20seek%20shelter.%20A%20state%20of%20emergency%20for%20the%20home%20front%20was%20activated.%20Airspace%20across%20the%20entire%20Middle%20East%20was%20temporarily%20closed%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-on-iran-flights-canceled-diverted-busiest-airspace-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecivilian%20air%20traffic%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20drastically%20curtailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcrete%20casualty%20figures%20from%20the%20current%20attacks%20can%20so%20far%20only%20be%20verified%20to%20a%20limited%20extent.%20Iranian%20sources%20report%20numerous%20dead%20and%20wounded%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20airstrikes%2C%20without%20publishing%20confirmed%20overall%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20analysts%20have%20said%20that%20Iran%20possesses%20the%20largest%20rocket%20arsenal%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20has%20deployed%20more%20than%201%2C500%20projectiles%20in%20previous%20waves%20of%20attacks.%20Even%20highly%20advanced%20defense%20systems%20cannot%20guarantee%20complete%20protection%20under%20such%20circumstances.%20An%20Israeli%20security%20analyst%20was%20quoted%20in%20local%20media%20as%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20prolonged%20military%20exchange.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20strikes%20Iran%20at%20a%20moment%20of%20extraordinary%20domestic%20political%20instability.%20Since%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20nationwide%20protests%20have%20been%20shaking%20the%20country.%20Human%20rights%20advocates%20speak%20of%20massive%20state%20violence%20against%20demonstrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHRANA%2C%20a%20U.S.-based%20human%20rights%20organization%20run%20by%20Iranians%2C%20has%20so%20far%20documented%20more%20than%207%2C000%20confirmed%20deaths%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20protests.%20U.S.%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20had%20killed%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%2032%2C000%20protesters.%26quot%3B%20The%20figure%20is%20based%20on%20estimates%20from%20Iranian%20health%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20public%20sentiment%20oscillates%20between%20approval%20and%20growing%20concern.%20Many%20Israelis%20view%20the%20strike%20as%20a%20necessary%20measure%20against%20a%20potentially%20nuclear-armed%20Iran.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20fears%20of%20regional%20escalation%20are%20growing%20%E2%80%94%20with%20possible%20attacks%20by%20Iranian-backed%20groups%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Iraq%2C%20or%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20Iranian%20retaliatory%20strikes%20have%20shown%20that%20even%20Israel's%20multi-layered%20air%20defense%20system%20cannot%20entirely%20prevent%20impacts.%20Yet%20everyday%20life%20continues.%20Schools%20remain%20partially%20closed%2C%20reservists%20are%20being%20called%20up%2C%20and%20businesses%20are%20operating%20in%20emergency%20mode.%20Between%20sirens%20and%20all-clears%2C%20a%20fragile%20normalcy%20is%20taking%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20countries%20called%20for%20immediate%20de-escalation.%20Diplomats%20warn%20that%20a%20direct%20military%20confrontation%20between%20Israel%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%20could%20trigger%20a%20regional%20war.%20An%20estimated%2040%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20U.S.%20troops%20are%20currently%20deployed%20in%20the%20broader%20region%2C%20supported%20by%20carrier%20strike%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20a%20military%20presence%20at%20its%20highest%20level%20in%20more%20than%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20days%20are%20considered%20critical%3A%20Will%20Iran%20expand%20its%20attacks%3F%20Will%20proxy%20militias%20such%20as%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20actively%20enter%20the%20conflict%3F%20Will%20the%20U.S.%20strikes%20remain%20limited%20%E2%80%94%20or%20is%20an%20open%20war%20beginning%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20all%20of%20this%20means%20above%20all%20one%20thing%3A%20living%20to%20the%20rhythm%20of%20the%20sirens.%20Many%20have%20already%20brought%20mattresses%20and%20water%20supplies%20into%20their%20shelters.%20No%20one%20knows%20when%20the%20next%20alarm%20will%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EConstantin%20Schreiber%20is%20a%20reporter%20for%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network.%20The%20network%20publishes%20major%20stories%20from%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20network%20of%20publications%2C%20a%20worldwide%20group%20of%20news%20outlets%20that%20includes%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftel-aviv-israel-dispatch-iran-counterattack-sirens-2026