n-tensions%2Farticleshow%2F128893894.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbaba-vanga-prediction-for-world-war-3-goes-viral-amid-usisrael-strikes-on-iran-and-pakistan-afghanistan-tensions%2Famp_articleshow%2F128893894.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbaba-vanga-prediction-for-world-war-3-goes-viral-amid-usisrael-strikes-on-iran-and-pakistan-afghanistan-tensions%2Famp_articleshow%2F128893894.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20campus%20tours%20filled%20our%20weekends%2C%20we%20began%20turning%20prospective%20college%20visits%20with%20our%20teens%20into%20family%20vacations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2fef1fb3fcb426486eca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20touring%20schools%20with%20our%20kids%20that%20we%20started%20turning%20prospective%20college%20visits%20into%20mini%20family%20vacations.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Barnes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESending%20two%20kids%20to%20college%20meant%20months%20of%20driving%20to%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-mom-made-college-tours-exciting-2025-4%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etouring%20campuses%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESo%2C%20I%20started%20turning%20our%20campus%20visits%20into%20%26quot%3Btour-cations%26quot%3B%20with%20day%20trips%20and%20fun%20local%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20learning%20about%20schools%2C%20we%20spent%20time%20together%20visiting%20local%20restaurants%20and%20attractions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20two%20kids%20were%20getting%20ready%20to%20choose%20their%20colleges%2C%20our%20family's%20schedule%20seemed%20to%20get%20busier%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20our%20school%20breaks%20and%20weekends%20were%20filled%20with%20the%20same%20monotonous%20routine%3A%20Drive%20several%20hours%20to%20a%20college%2C%20take%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20campus%2C%20and%20head%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20were%20these%20visits%20pretty%20rushed%20and%20stressful%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20monopolizing%20our%20free%20time%20as%20a%20family%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20vacation%20time%20we'd%20lost%20and%20make%20these%20visits%20even%20more%20valuable%2C%20I%20began%20completely%20changing%20how%20we%20planned%20%E2%80%94%20and%20viewed%20%E2%80%94%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-tour-guide-tips-campus-visit-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecombined%20campus%20tours%20with%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20began%20going%20on%20%26quot%3Btour-cations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a443e9b-a12c-4be4-a7c1-e657c39bc35d%5C%22%3ETurning%20college%20visits%20into%20mini%20vacations%20took%20work%2C%20but%20it%20paid%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222729%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20and%20kid%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f306de8408f6671803e1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223321%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuring%20one%20trip%20to%20look%20at%20colleges%2C%20we%20stopped%20in%20Paris%2C%20Tennessee.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Barnes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20schools%20we%20visited%20were%20within%20five%20hours%20of%20our%20home%2C%20so%20we%20started%20staying%20in%20the%20area%20overnight%20so%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20drive%20back%20after%20a%20long%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20we%20stayed%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-hotels-in-american-college-towns-2013-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon-campus%20hotels%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20save%20money%20on%20parking%20and%20have%20easy%20access%20to%20our%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20possible%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20combine%20colleges%20that%20were%20relatively%20close%20to%20each%20other%20into%20one%20itinerary.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20trip%20included%20the%20University%20of%20Mississippi%2C%20Mississippi%20State%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbama-rush-university-alabama-sorority-racism-segregation-discrimination-history-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Alabama%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Another%20focused%20on%20Georgia%20Tech%2C%20Emory%20University%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Tennessee%20-%20Knoxville.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20each%20trip%2C%20I%20laid%20out%20the%20destinations%20on%20the%20map%20as%20if%20we%20were%20going%20on%20a%20European%20vacation%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-luxury-carnival-cruise-line-seabourn-plans-world-cruises-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecruise%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20planning%20around%20VIP%20tours%2C%20honors-college%20visits%2C%20meals%20with%20current%20students%2C%20and%20admitted-student%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20scheduling%20our%20on-campus%20sessions%2C%20I%20was%20also%20researching%20local%20recommendations%20in%20the%20towns%20near%20each%20school%20and%20along%20our%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20our%20best%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20both%20our%20time%20on%20the%20road%20and%20near%20each%20school.%20We%20toured%20space%20centers%2C%20attended%20baseball%20games%2C%20stopped%20at%20dairy%20farms%2C%20found%20local%20gems%20we%20still%20dine%20at%20today%2C%20and%20even%20went%20on%20small%20day%20trips%20to%20see%20special%20landmarks%2C%20including%20the%20replica%20Eiffel%20Tower%20in%20Paris%2C%20Tennessee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ate%20in%20every%20college%20cafeteria%20while%20trying%20local%20off-campus%20favorites%2C%20from%20the%20iconic%20doughnuts%20at%20Mary%20Lou's%20near%20Purdue%20University%20to%20the%20memorable%20bites%20at%20Dreamland%20BBQ%2C%20just%20minutes%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Alabama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20and%20kid%20smiling%20with%20hot%20dogs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f306d1fb3fcb426486ee0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20made%20sure%20to%20try%20the%20famous%20Denny%20Dogs%20at%20a%20University%20of%20Alabama%20-%20Tuscaloosa%20baseball%20game.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Barnes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-touring-colleges-daughter-bonding-brought-closer-together-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20colleges%20closer%20to%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20approached%20our%20tours%20with%20a%20similar%20spirit%20of%20adventure%2C%20doing%20my%20best%20to%20find%20new-to-us%20restaurants%20and%20cool%20attractions%20or%20shops%20we%20could%20check%20out%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20nice%20to%20have%20a%20plan%2C%20but%20I%20also%20found%20some%20of%20our%20most%20fun%20moments%20occurred%20when%20we%20got%20lost%20or%20simply%20asked%20the%20student%20tour%20guides%20where%20their%20favorite%20local%20spots%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22898986f0-2e13-4490-8a1e-07b14bff5c9c%5C%22%3EOur%20vacation-style%20college%20visits%20were%20a%20huge%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20standing%20at%20California%20Dreamin%20Castle%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f30b91fb3fcb426486eeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20stopped%20at%20local%20restaurants%20throughout%20our%20trips.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Barnes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20glamorous%20beach%20vacations%20are%20great%2C%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20get%20to%20explore%20colleges%20and%20their%20surrounding%20areas%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20were%20able%20to%20get%20a%20better%20view%20of%20where%20they%20might%20live%20for%20several%20years%2C%20and%20we%20parents%20gained%20more%20perspective%20about%20where%20they%20could%20end%20up%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBest%20of%20all%2C%20we%20got%20to%20spend%20time%20together.%20These%20little%20trips%20would%20be%20some%20of%20the%20last%20we'd%20take%20as%20a%20family%20before%20planning%20got%20more%20complicated%20with%20school%20breaks%20and%20busy%20work%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20both%20kids%20chose%20schools%20we%20%26quot%3Btour-cationed%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20hope%20the%20memories%20we%20made%20on%20our%20first%20visits%20last%20far%20beyond%20their%20college%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturned-college-tours-into-family-vacations-tourcations-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772301721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f392de8408f6671803f68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturned-college-tours-into-family-vacations-tourcations-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20visiting%20prospective%20colleges%20with%20our%20kids%20that%20we%20began%20planning%20%26quot%3Btour-cations%26quot%3B%20to%20combine%20campus%20tours%20with%20family%20vacations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Amy%20Barnes)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturned-college-tours-into-family-vacations-tourcations-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22