https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a2f7aefd4fbd083f29453a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20list%20of%20canceled%20flights%20from%20the%20main%20airport%20in%20Beirut%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20on%20Saturday.%3Cp%3EHoussam%20Shbaro%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMore%20than%20100%20flights%20have%20been%20diverted%20to%20dozens%20of%20different%20destinations%20after%20strikes%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20created%20a%20map%20showing%20where%20some%20of%20the%20planes%20ended%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMuscat%2C%20Oman%2C%20was%20the%20most%20common%20destination%20%E2%80%94%20but%20dozens%20more%20returned%20to%20their%20origins%20or%20unexpected%20regions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Israel's%20strikes%20on%20Iran%20have%20thrown%20global%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-us-strike-iran-preemptive-defense-chief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eair%20travel%20into%20chaos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20strikes%2C%20at%20least%20145%20flights%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20been%20diverted%20to%2073%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20compiled%20a%20map%20showing%20where%20some%20of%20the%20diverted%20planes%20have%20ended%20up%20as%20of%209%3A30%20a.m.%20EST.%20To%20compile%20the%20data%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20Flightradar24's%20arrivals%20lists%20for%20five%20major%20airports%20in%20the%20region%3A%20Dubai%20International%2C%20Doha%20International%20Airport%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%20International%20Airport%2C%20Sharjah%20International%20Airport%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20and%20Bahrain%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lists%20show%20that%2063%20flights%20have%20been%20diverted%20from%20Doha%2C%2047%20from%20Dubai%20International%2C%2016%20from%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%2016%20from%20Sharjah%2C%20and%20three%20from%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20map%20shows%20where%20those%20flights%20landed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOcmnK%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20of%20the%20world%20showing%20where%20flights%20diverted%20to%20after%20us%20strikes%20on%20Iran%20on%20February%2028%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOcmnK%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20likely%20more%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eflights%20that%20are%20affected%20and%20that%20Flightradar24%20had%20not%20yet%20registered%20as%20diverted%20or%20that%20were%20bound%20for%20other%20destinations%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20flights%20that%20diverted%20didn't%20have%20to%20change%20course%20too%20dratsically.%20The%20most%20common%20airport%20to%20which%20flights%20were%20diverted%20was%20Muscat%2C%20Oman%2C%20accounting%20for%2017%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2011%20landed%20in%20Istanbul%20and%20Karachi%2C%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9e63f18-d022-4fd3-a85c-9f4aea119a55%5C%22%3EAir%20travel%20chaos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFlights%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20frequently%20fly%20to%20and%20across%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20congested%20airspace%20and%20global%20airlines%20like%20Qatar%20Airways%2C%20Emirates%2C%20Etihad%20Airways%2C%20and%20Saudia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20these%20carriers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F15-hour-flight-to-nowhere-iran-strike-qatar-airline-chaos-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediverted%20dozens%20of%20planes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Data%20from%20the%20aviation%20analytics%20firm%20shows%20some%203%2C400%20scheduled%20flights%20were%20destined%20for%20the%20region%20today%3B%20it's%20likely%20many%20of%20those%20that%20haven't%20taken%20off%20yet%20will%20be%20canceled%20so%20long%20as%20the%20airspace%20remains%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiversions%20are%20costly%20because%20airlines%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20extra%20fuel%2C%20labor%2C%20and%20any%20passenger%20compensation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-integrated-operations-center-dispatch-delays-cancellations-weather-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirline%20operations%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20play%20Tetris%20to%20manage%20cancellations%2C%20delays%2C%20and%20misplaced%20crews%20%E2%80%94%20are%20likely%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20chaos.%20Planes%20landing%20in%20unintended%20destinations%20can%20have%20knock-on%20effects%20on%20their%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20flights%20had%20to%20return%20to%20their%20origins%20or%20ended%20up%20in%20unexpected%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20to%20Doha%20U-turned%20over%20Ireland%20and%20looked%20set%20to%20land%20back%20in%20Philadelphia%20after%2013%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20other%20US%20flights%20landed%20across%20Europe.%20An%20Emirates%20flight%20from%20Seattle%20diverted%20to%20Warsaw%2C%20Poland%2C%20and%20another%2C%20from%20New%20York%2C%20went%20to%20Vienna.%20Other%20airplanes%20landed%20in%20places%20like%20Rome%20and%20Madrid%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20diversions%20also%20included%20a%20private%20jet%2C%20a%20Bombardier%20Global%207500%2C%20which%20was%20heading%20from%20Geneva%20to%20Sharjah%20but%20diverted%20to%20Cairo%2C%20per%20Flightradar24.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strikes-flight-diversions-map-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772300577000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a32798fd4fbd083f294692%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22origi