m%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpakistan-owned-roosevelt-hotel-owes-nyc-14-6m-despite-migrant-shelter-windfall-report%2Farticleshow%2F128891477.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpakistan-owned-roosevelt-hotel-owes-nyc-14-6m-despite-migrant-shelter-windfall-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F128891477.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fpakistan-owned-roosevelt-hotel-owes-nyc-14-6m-despite-migrant-shelter-windfall-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F128891477.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20go%20clubbing%20with%20my%204%20daughters%20in%20matching%20outfits.%20It's%20got%20us%20through%20hard%20times.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221322%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20at%20club%20with%20daughters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698e0566d3c7faef0ece2884%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJen%20Dixon%20goes%20dancing%20with%20her%20four%20daughters.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jen%20Dixon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJen%20Dixon%2C%2056%2C%20from%20Sydney%2C%20regularly%20goes%20clubbing%20with%20her%20four%20daughters%2C%20ages%2019%2C%2021%2C%2023%2C%20and%2025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20go%20in%20matching%20costumes%20and%20sing%20songs%20from%20their%20favourite%20shows%20together%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETheir%20unique%20shared%20passion%20has%20gotten%20them%20through%20some%20dark%20times%20and%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jen%20Dixon.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-things-people-do-at-clubs-from-a-dj-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20out%20to%20nightclubs%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20four%20daughters%2C%20and%20we%20often%20coordinate%20outfits.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nightclub%20event%20we%20attend%20together%20most%20often%20has%20a%20unique%20twist%3A%20it%20only%20plays%20songs%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-musical-movies-based-on-broadway-shows-and-worst-films-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emusical%20theatre%20productions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musical%20theatre%20holds%20a%20special%20place%20in%20our%20family.%20It%20has%20gotten%20us%20through%20some%20tough%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202784452-a27d-40d4-a630-3aac314a1e09%5C%22%3EIt%20all%20started%20with%20'Wicked'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%2015%20years%20ago%20when%20we%20saw%20the%20theatre%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BWicked%3Cem%3E.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20became%20obsessed.%20We'd%20belt%20songs%20from%20it%20around%20the%20house%2C%20and%20the%20girls%20started%20learning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-who-learned-to-play-musical-instruments-for-movies-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplay%20different%20musical%20instruments%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20piano%2C%20trumpet%2C%20and%20flute.%20They'd%20dress%20up%20and%20put%20on%20a%20performance%20every%20Christmas.%20The%20festive%20atmosphere%20prepared%20us%20for%20life's%20blows%20that%20were%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20girls%20got%20older%2C%20our%20shared%20love%20of%20music%20led%20us%20to%20attend%20concerts%20and%20festivals%20together.%20Then%2C%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20everything%20changed.%20My%20eldest%20daughter%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-judge-noah-mcadams-chemotherapy-leukemia-ruling-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ediagnosed%20with%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20acute%20lymphoblastic%20leukemia.%20It%20was%20such%20a%20shock%20since%20she%20was%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20really%20scary%20time.%20She%20lost%20all%20her%20hair%20and%20eyebrows%2C%20her%20face%20swelled%20up%2C%20and%20she%20spent%20a%20full%20year%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20how%20amazing%20her%20school%20was%3A%20when%20she%20was%20down%20and%20completely%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoey-king-shaved-head-cancer-tweets-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20bald%20from%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20knowing%20musicals%20were%20her%20safe%20space%2C%20just%20as%20she%20left%20the%20hospital%2C%20they%20cast%20her%20in%20the%20school%20production%20of%20%26quot%3BHairspray.%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20irony%20wasn't%20lost%20on%20us%2C%20and%20gave%20us%20a%20much-needed%20giggle.%20Her%20wig%20for%20the%20show%20was%20huge%20and%20fabulous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20each%20daughter%20brings%20something%20unique%20to%20the%20singing%20around%20the%20house.%20The%20eldest%20has%20perfect%20pitch%2C%20a%20beautiful%20voice%2C%20and%20a%20knack%20for%20singing%20herself%20into%20better%20spirits.%20One%20has%20an%20encyclopedic%20memory%20for%20lyrics.%20The%20five%20of%20us%20are%20like%20an%20all-female%20musical%20troupe%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20for%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don't%20take%20ourselves%20too%20seriously.%20My%20husband%20just%20smiles.%20It's%20not%20his%20thing!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274032f4e-6e42-4413-b005-cb90f005ccf8%5C%22%3EI%20found%20a%20club%20where%20we%20could%20dress%20up%20and%20dance%20to%20showtunes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20my%20eldest%20was%20going%20into%20remission%2C%20another%20setback%20happened.%20My%20second%20daughter%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20autism%20spectrum%20disorder%2C%20ADHD%2C%20and%20severe%20depression.%20She'd%20masked%20symptoms%2C%20as%20many%20girls%20do%2C%20then%20crashed%20and%20burned.%20It's%20been%20a%20real%20journey%2C%20learning%20how%20this%20impacts%20her%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20desperately%20needed%20some%20joy%20back%20into%20our%20lives.%20It's%20then%20I%20came%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clubbroadway.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClub%20Broadway%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20social%20media.%20It%20seemed%20designed%20for%20us%3A%20the%20founder%2C%20DJ%20Dan%20Murphy%2C%20plays%20showtunes%20all%20night%2C%20and%20it%20tours%20around%20Australia.%20We%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20go%20to%20the%20next%20one%20in%20Sydney.%20I'm%20a%20former%20textiles%20teacher%2C%20so%20I%20got%20to%20making%20our%20outfits.%20I%20love%20a%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20as%20the%20tin%20man%2C%20and%20will%20never%20forget%20walking%20through%20the%20streets%20of%20Sydney%20with%20one%20daughter%20as%20Elpheba%20and%20one%20as%20Glinda%20from%20%26quot%3BWicked%3Cem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20daughter%20as%20Dorothy%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wizard%20of%20Oz%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20my%20second%20daughter%20decided%20to%20go%20as%20a%20character%20from%20the%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EBook%20of%20Mormon.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20didn't%20think%20the%20girls%20would%20come%20with%20me%20to%20the%20next%20one%2C%20even%20though%20I%20secretly%20wished%20they%20would.%20It%20was%20like%20bottled%20serotonin%20where%20closet%20lifelong%20theatre%20nuts%20like%20me%20can%20find%20our%20people.%20To%20my%20delighted%20surprise%2C%20they%20agreed%20to%20come%20to%20the%20next%20one%20%E2%80%94%20and%20every%20one%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20street%20cred%20of%20being%20seen%20out%20clubbing%20with%20your%20mom%20in%20coordinating%20costumes%2C%20all%20four%20of%20my%20girls%20are%20so%20confident%20in%20who%20they%20are%3B%20they%20don't%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20musical%20theatre%20community%20here%20in%20Australia%20has%20given%20me%20a%20whole%20new%20friendship%20group%2C%20too%2C%20in%20case%20my%20daughters%20one%20day%20decide%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20clubbing%20with%20their%20mom.%20That%20seems%20way%20off%2C%20though.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Sound%20of%20Music%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20my%20next%20dress-up%20project.%20I'm%20going%20to%20persuade%20the%20girls%20to%20go%20as%20the%20Von%20Trapps.%20As%20a%20singing%20family%20that%20supports%20each%20other%20through%20hard%20times%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20most%20fitting%20one%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-goes-clubbing-with-kids-regularly-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772297701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698e05b4d3c7faef0ece288d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-goes-clubbing-with-kids-regularly-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20mom%20shares%20how%20attending%20musical%20theatre%20club%20nights%20with%20her%20four%20daughters%20helped%20her%20family%20heal%20through%20cancer%20and%20mental%20health%20struggles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Gary%20Nunn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-goes-clubbing-with-kids-regularly-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Nobody%20asked%20Hrithik%20if%20he%20agreed%20with%20politics%20of%20Dhurandhar'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772297072000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128892085%2Cimgsize-51858.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnobody-asked-hrithik-roshan-if-he-agreed-with-politics-of-dhurandhar-hype-around-akshaye-khanna-was-manipulative-says-shobhaa-de%2Farticleshow%2F128891755.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F128891755.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20journalist%20Shobhaa%20