hy-salad-greens-are-good-for-brain-health-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esomething%20green%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it's%20chicken%2C%20I%20might%20add%20some%20broccoli%2C%20if%20it's%20spaghetti%2C%20let's%20dish%20up%20a%20side%20of%20green%20beans.%20I'm%20not%20perfect%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I%20think%20any%20little%20effort%20helps.%20When%20I%20make%20tacos%20now%2C%20I%20mix%20the%20ground%20beef%20with%20some%20mashed%20black%20beans.%20That%20way%2C%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20less%20meat%2C%20but%20also%20you're%20getting%20fiber%20from%20the%20beans.%20I%20haven't%20overhauled%20my%20diet%20completely%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20finding%20the%20little%20evidence-backed%20opportunities%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20honestly%20a%20more%20realistic%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mark%20active%20dad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cf28aefb52c8bd0deb9f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222306%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExercise%2C%20a%20healthy%20diet%2C%20and%20managing%20stress%20have%20all%20been%20important%20to%20my%20recovery.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mark%20Seguin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20five%20years%20since%20my%20cancer%20diagnosis%20now%2C%20and%20I'm%20almost%20in%20the%20clear.%20My%20doctors%20say%20if%20my%20next%20scan%20looks%20good%2C%20and%20my%20blood%20work%20remains%20clean%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20release%20me%20completely.%20It's%20kind%20of%20a%20scary%20prospect%20to%20go%20out%20into%20the%20open%20world%20without%20your%20oncology%20team%20looking%20out%20for%20cancer.%20I've%20found%20peace%20knowing%20I%20am%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20we%20know%20decrease%20the%20odds%20of%20recurrence%3A%20exercising%20more%2C%20eating%20better%2C%20and%20decreasing%20stress.%20I%20also%20take%20a%20baby%20aspirin%2C%20which%20recent%20studies%20have%20suggested%20may%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20recurrence%20of%20certain%20types%20of%20colon%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d5c9cca-167d-462f-8318-f047a0d9761e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20rules%20to%20live%20by%20for%20finding%20colon%20cancer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221727%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mark%20with%20screening%20at%2045%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1e2bffd4fbd083f2938a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221295%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you're%2045%2C%20get%20a%20colonoscopy.%20Don't%20delay%20the%20care%20that%20could%20save%20your%20life.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mark%20Seguin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20always%20remember%20a%20few%20things%20that%20can%20help%20identify%20colon%20cancer%20early%2C%20and%20share%20them%20with%20my%20friends%20when%20I%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20if%20something%20feels%20off%2C%20go%20get%20it%20checked%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESecond%3A%20make%20that%20follow-up%20appointment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20doctor%20said%20the%20one%20thing%20I%20did%20that%20so%20many%20folks%20miss%20is%20actually%20going%20in%20for%20that%20next%20appointment%2C%20after%20leaving%20the%20ER.%20Don't%20delay%20the%20care%20that%20might%20save%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFinally%2C%20if%20you're%2045%2C%20get%20a%20colonoscopy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%2C%20we%20snowboarders%20like%20to%20tough%20things%20out%20sometimes.%20Don't%20do%20that%20with%20your%20colon.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20you're%2045%2C%20right%3F%20Did%20you%20get%20that%20colonoscopy%20booked%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mark%20and%20kids%20snowboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cf28defb52c8bd0deb9fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20still%20love%20to%20snowboard%2C%20and%20try%20to%20bring%20my%20colon%20cancer%20advocacy%20to%20the%20slopes%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mark%20Seguin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20keep%20it%20casual%20and%20not%20be%20the%20colon%20cancer%20weirdo%20out%20on%20the%20slopes%2C%20but%20I%20do%20want%20to%20advocate%20for%20more%20awareness%20of%20young%20colon%20cancer.%20Colon%20cancer%20is%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-leading-cause-cancer-death-under-50-shocking-experts-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20cause%20of%20cancer%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20people%20under%2050%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20only%20cancer%20that's%20becoming%20more%20deadly%20in%20my%20age%20group%2C%20not%20less.%20If%20I%20can%20help%20one%20more%20person%20get%20checked%20and%20find%20cancer%20earlier%2C%20that's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FjXZaBv3po-4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Life%20Lessons%20From%20Young%20Colon%20Cancer%20Patients%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiagnosed-with-colon-cancer-only-had-one-symptom-stomach-pain-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772295901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699cf326efb52c8bd0deba1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiagnosed-with-colon-cancer-only-had-one-symptom-stomach