ia.com%2F332196%2Fvidyasagar-hariharan-flamingos-mumbai-thane-creek-conserve-wetlands-wildlife-photography%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epanoramic%20views%20and%20is%20perfect%20for%20photography%20lovers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnjoy%20a%20local%20lunch%20and%20return%20to%20your%20hotel%20for%20some%20downtime.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20consider%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20nearby%20temple%20or%20small%20garden%20if%20travelling%20with%20elders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%205%3A%20Souvenir%20shopping%20and%20return%20to%20Mumbai%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20your%20final%20morning%2C%20explore%20Panvel%20Market%20for%20souvenirs%20such%20as%20local%20spices%2C%20papads%2C%20dried%20snacks%2C%20or%20handmade%20goods.%20Many%20families%20also%20pick%20up%20fresh%20fruit%20or%20jaggery%20as%20gifts%20or%20travel%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoard%20a%20local%20train%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20with%20your%20bags%20a%20little%20fuller%20and%20hearts%20refreshed%20from%20five%20days%20of%20greenery%2C%20light%20trekking%2C%20and%20family%20bonding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T215224.548_11zon-1756743769.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Karnala%20Bird%20Sanctuary%20is%20home%20to%20over%20150%20species%20of%20resident%20and%20migratory%20birds%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Surojit%20Palmal%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T215224.548_11zon-1756743769.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T215