l%20grass%20skirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20mythological%20characters%20spring%20to%20life%2C%20delighting%20both%20children%20and%20adults%20with%20their%20playful%20presence.%20Moving%20from%20house%20to%20house%2C%20the%20dancers%20narrate%20stories%20through%20expressive%20gestures%20and%20rhythmic%20steps%2C%20often%20accompanied%20by%20folk%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20entertainment%2C%20%3Cem%3EKummatti%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%20helps%20preserve%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20oral%20traditions%2C%20keeping%20alive%20the%20tales%20and%20artistry%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kummatti%20Kali%20adds%20whimsy%20to%20Onam%2C%20with%20dancers%20wearing%20wooden%20masks%20and%20colourful%20grass%20skirts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fonam-2_11zon-1757051553-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496739%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKummatti%20Kali%20%3C%2Fem%3Eadds%20whimsy%20to%20Onam%2C%20with%20dancers%20wearing%20wooden%20masks%20and%20colourful%20grass%20skirts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFolk%20songs%3